ggtree分析群落多样性数据

Gao, Chun-Hui

2018年4月3日

需要用ggtree来画一幅图

ggtree不仅支持nwk等树格式，还支持多个进化分析软件的输出结果。使用输出结果，可以在绘图中使用meta信息。

setwd("H:/Spring_Work/35. 研究数据/2018-4-3 ggtree")
library(ggtree)
## Loading required package: ggplot2
## Loading required package: treeio
## ggtree v1.10.5  For help: https://guangchuangyu.github.io/ggtree
## 
## If you use ggtree in published research, please cite:
## Guangchuang Yu, David Smith, Huachen Zhu, Yi Guan, Tommy Tsan-Yuk Lam. ggtree: an R package for visualization and annotation of phylogenetic trees with their covariates and other associated data. Methods in Ecology and Evolution 2017, 8(1):28-36, doi:10.1111/2041-210X.12628
tree <- read.tree(file="otu_reps-isolates.nwk")
tree$tip.label <- gsub("(OTU\\d+)_.*","\\1",tree$tip.label,perl=TRUE)
tree$tip.label <- gsub("^.*?_","",tree$tip.label)

ggtree = ggplot() + geom_tree() + theme_tree()

ggtree(tree,layout = "fan")

读取分类信息

# 读取分类信息
tax <- read.delim(file="taxonomy_classification.txt")
# 调整分类信息的名称，使其与树的编号保持一致
rownames(tax) <- gsub(" ", "_", tax$full_name)
# 获取分类信息不全的OTU

# 为了更好的显示效果，需要将分类信息不全的OTU在树中去掉
unclassified_otu <- rownames(tax[tax$genus =="",])
tree <- drop.tip(tree,unclassified_otu)
tax <- tax[tax$genus != "",]

# 将树上的Nodes进行归类
groupinfo <- split(rownames(tax),tax$phylum)
# groupOTU将树种的OTU分配group属性
tree <- groupOTU(tree, groupinfo)
ggtree(tree,layout = 'fan',size=1.5,aes(color=group))+theme(legend.position = "right")

整合OTU热图

# 读取OTU表
otu_table <- read.delim("otu_table.txt",row.names = "OTU",header = T)

# 去除不含分类信息的行
idx <- which(rownames(otu_table) %in% unclassified_otu)
otu_table <- otu_table[-idx,]

# 标准化：将count转变为百分比
norm <- t(t(otu_table)/colSums(otu_table,na=T))*100
# 筛选树中OTU对应的数据(由于tax中不仅包含OTU还包含了isolates，这一步运行会报错)
# tax_per <- norm[rownames(tax),]
p <- ggtree(tree,aes(color=group),size=1.5) + geom_tiplab(size=1,align = TRUE,linesize = 0.5)
## Warning: The plyr::rename operation has created duplicates for the
## following name(s): (`size`)
# 绘制热图和树
gheatmap(p,norm,offset = .15,width = 0.3,font.size = 2,colnames_angle = -45,hjust = -0.1)

# 按组求OTU丰度均值
# 设置分组信息
meta <- data.frame(row.names = c("D1a","D1b","D2a","D2b","D4a","D4b","D7a","D7b"),group = c("D1","D1","D2","D2","D4","D4","D7","D7"))
# OTU表转置，以样品名为行
mat_t <- t(norm)
# 合并分组信息到OTU表，并去除样品名列
mat_t2 <- merge(meta,mat_t,by="row.names")[,-1]
# 按组求平均值
mat_mean <- aggregate(mat_t2[,-1],by=mat_t2[1],FUN = mean)
# 去除非数据列并转置
mat_mean_final <- do.call(rbind,mat_mean)[-1,]
# 重命名rownames为分组
colnames(mat_mean_final) <- mat_mean$group
# 按组均值绘制热图和树
gheatmap(p,mat_mean_final,offset=0.05,width = 0.1,font.size = 2,colnames_angle = -45,hjust = -0.1)

# 标度转换后重新绘图
mat_mean_final_log <- log10(mat_mean_final)
gheatmap(p,mat_mean_final_log,offset=0.05,width = 0.1,font.size = 2,colnames_angle = -45,hjust = -0.1)
